title: Beautiful One Bedroom in Downtown Renton
posting_body: ['This lovely community is centrally located in Renton to provide easy access to both work and play throughout the city and surrounding area.', 'Each exquisite home offers modern fixtures and fine finishes to fit every individual lifestyle, while still accommodating the ease of adding your own personal touches throughout your new home.', 'You’ll find a wonderful array of amenities including 9 ft elevated ceilings, cozy living room fireplaces, and a fitness studio.', '-Professional Caring Management Team', '-Relaxing Hot Spa (Revo 225 only)', '-Surrounded by Gourmet Restaurants & Sophisticated Shops', '-Additional Exterior Storage', "-Chef's Kitchen with Energy Efficient Appliances, including Refrigerator/Freezer, Dishwasher, Microwave & Range", '-Build Your Credit with RentPlus', '-BBQ Grilling Stations', '-Easy Access to I-5, WA-167 & Public Transportation', '-Pet Friendly Community', '-Smart Home Features with Mobile Controls', '-Ample Storage, with Linen, Coat, & Large Bedroom Closets', '-Security Deposit Options Offered through Jetty', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Prices and Availability are Subject to Change Without Notice']
